Class Observatory

java.lang.Object

@Entity @VoDml(id="proposal:Observatory", role=objectType) public class Observatory extends Organization implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>, org.ivoa.vodml.jaxb.XmlIdManagement
